    These videos are freely available online at Grand Valley's Department of Mathematics YouTube channel on this playlist:
  </p>
  <p>
    \url{http://gvsu.edu/s/0l1} These online videos were created and developed by Dr.
    Robert Talbert of Grand Valley State University.
  </p>
